OL,3,CLabour MP: 'I stand clear of platform
OL,4,Cedges after death threats'
OL,6,FA Labour MP has warned there is
OL,7,Finsufficient security for MPs who
OL,8,Freceive death threats.
OL,10,FBarry Sheerman said he had become a
OL,11,Fperson who "watches where he walks" as
OL,12,Fa result of intimidation. He said
OL,13,Fthere was a lack of support for
OL,14,Fpoliticians "on the receiving end".
OL,16,FIn December the Huddersfield MP said
OL,17,Fhe was left "absolutely haunted" after
OL,18,Fa man threatened to come to London and
OL,19,Fkill him.
