OL,6,FAt the time he suggested more help
OL,7,Fshould be available on the mental
OL,8,Fhealth impact of such an experience.
OL,10,FOn Thursday Mr Sheerman told MPs: "I
OL,11,Fknow some Members of the House will
OL,12,Fknow that I had a death threat. A
OL,13,Fgentleman was arrested and went into a
OL,14,Fmental institution.
OL,16,F"When he was released the House
OL,17,Fauthorities and the Met Police met me
OL,18,Fand said this gentleman is now out,
OL,19,Fand he knows where you live."
