OL,6,FAddressing Conservative MP Sir Charles
OL,7,FWalker, who represents the House of
OL,8,FCommons Commission, Mr Sheerman added:
OL,9,F"It is very stressful and I have to
OL,10,Fsay all that has been said by him, I
OL,11,Fknow he believes it and he is
OL,12,Fpassionate about it, but it doesn't
OL,13,Ffeel like there is very much there on
OL,14,Fthe receiving end."
OL,16,FSir Charles replied: "I am so sorry
OL,17,Fthat he has experienced this after
OL,18,Fgiving more than 40 years of service
OL,19,Fto this Parliament and this country.
