OL,6,FCommons Speaker Sir Lindsay Hoyle
OL,7,Fadded: "Security of all members really
OL,8,Fmatters. It is taken very seriously in
OL,9,Fthis House. It is ongoing and I am
OL,10,Fhaving serious conversations about
OL,11,Fwhat we do going forward.
OL,13,F"What I can tell you is we have some
OL,14,Fof the best people working on it, and
OL,15,FI would like to thank them for what
OL,16,Fthey do."
