OL,6,FThe continued warnings about MPs'
OL,7,Fsecurity comes the day after ,
OL,8,Fsuggesting he was concerned some MPs
OL,9,Fcould be subject to intimidation as a
OL,10,Fresult of their views on the Middle
OL,11,FEast conflict.
OL,13,FTory backbencher Tobias Ellwood's home
OL,14,Fwas targeted earlier this month by pro-
OL,15,FPalestine protesters, with the police
OL,16,Fwarning his family to "stay away" from
OL,17,Fthe property as "arriving through that
OL,18,Fcrowd would've antagonised the
OL,19,Fsituation".
